name: Lactate shuttle #2
description:
Sustaining high levels of lactate requires specific training. This ability to tolerate lactate only comes with precise intervals in training. 



We can all produce a one-off effort to build lactate. With carefully planned intervals, we can maintain this high lactate level for an extended period. This is where the training effect happens!
